function [map] = TFClustMatrixCmap(csize)
% /VOLUMES/SRAMSEY/PROJECTS/MACNET/MATLAB/SCRIPTS/TFCLUSTMATRIXCMAP - Colormap
%   usage: /Volumes/sramsey/Projects/MacNet/Matlab/Scripts/TFClustMatrixCmap - returns a colormap the same length as the
%               current figure's colormap.
%          /Volumes/sramsey/Projects/MacNet/Matlab/Scripts/TFClustMatrixCmap(M) - returns an M x 3 sized colormap.
